org.javaToAvalla.model.terms

Class AvallaCheckTerm

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.javaToAvalla.model.terms.Term
      • org.javaToAvalla.model.terms.AvallaTerm
        • org.javaToAvalla.model.terms.AvallaCheckTerm

  • public class AvallaCheckTerm
extends AvallaTerm
    Represents a check term in the Avalla language, which compares two terms: a left term and a right term.

    This class stores two string values: the left term and the right term, and provides methods to retrieve and modify these values.
